    <item>
      <title>韩国誓言采取严厉行动恢复市场秩序，结束不当行为</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/korea-vows-tough-actions-to-restore-market-order-end-misconduct</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国最高金融监管机构表示，如果金融公司发放过高利率或逃避其他责任，将面临“严厉措施”，这一措辞强硬的警告是为了在最近对该行业进行调查时恢复投资者信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/korea-vows-tough-actions-to-restore-market-order-end-misconduct</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 02:31:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>银行破坏了私人信贷创纪录的阿多纳交易 20 亿美元债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/banks-spoil-private-credit-s-record-ardonagh-deal-with-2-billion-bond</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ardonagh Group Ltd. 计划最早于周一发行 20 亿美元的债券，这是银行战胜私人信贷公司的一次关键胜利，后者曾向这家英国保险公司提供了创纪录的 50 亿美元贷款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/banks-spoil-private-credit-s-record-ardonagh-deal-with-2-billion-bond</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 02:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管北京承诺保持稳定，中国股市仍大幅波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-stocks-languish-despite-renewed-vow-to-stabilize-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继上周暴跌后，中国股市周一再次陷入波动，投资者评估了政策制定者稳定暴跌股市的最新承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/china-stocks-languish-despite-renewed-vow-to-stabilize-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:50:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市暴跌：监管机构誓言稳定市场，但未提供细节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-vows-to-stabilize-markets-offers-no-detail-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周五股价跌至五年低点后，中国证监会周日誓言要稳定市场，但政策制定者没有具体说明他们计划如何结束抛售。斯蒂芬·恩格尔在彭博电视台进行报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-02-05/china-vows-to-stabilize-markets-offers-no-detail-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 01:04:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔在“60分钟”节目中表示美联储对降息过早持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/powell-tells-60-minutes-fed-likely-to-wait-beyond-march-to-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，美国人可能要等到 3 月份之后央行才会降息，因为官员们正在寻找更多经济数据来确认通胀率将降至 2%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-05/powell-tells-60-minutes-fed-likely-to-wait-beyond-march-to-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Feb 2024 00:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对胡塞武装的袭击加剧紧张局势，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美国誓言对伊朗军队和代理人进行更多打击，而胡塞武装承诺对周末的轰炸进行报复，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 23:26:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔和中国小型股下滑导致美国国债下跌：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，政策制定者可能会等到三月之后再降息，随后美国国债延续了周五的抛售。尽管有官方支持的迹象，但市场不安情绪持续存在，中国小盘股下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/treasury-selloff-hits-asia-on-pared-rate-cut-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Feb 2024 22:33:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场降息押注因鲍威尔的抵制和就业而紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-04/bond-market-rate-cut-bets-rattled-by-powell-pushback-job-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国经济正在考验债券交易员对美联储今年将实施一系列降息的信心。]]></description>
